snippet.textDisplay:
He appears in the hearts. He comes so secretly to some that there is no movement, just His fragrant presence. It has tremendous pressure that is only felt by a loving heart who fears losing Him. Yet He makes other beloveds of His know, with certainty, about Himself in this way: Auliyaa have said His revelation is like one who is hit feels the strike of one who had struck. There are no confusions then, just unity with Him and His creation.
"Woh dekhta hai ghairon se kyun dil lagate ho
Jo kuch buton mein pate ho, us mein woh kya nahi"
